body:
**Input:**

```javascript
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "span": {
        "first": {
          "endPositionLte": 2,
          "operator": {
            "term": {
              "path": "title",
              "query": "dance"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$limit": 5
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 0,
      "title": 1
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[
  { title: 'Dance Program' },
  { title: 'Slam Dance' },
  { title: 'Last Dance' },
  { title: 'War Dance' },
  { title: 'Delhi Dance' }
]
```

MongoDB Search returns the documents that contain search word `dance`
in the first or second position of the `title` field.
